<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirm your email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', 'Comic Sans', cursive, sans-serif;
            background: #f1f8fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 45px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 73, 124, 0.12);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .email-header .logo { font-size: 3em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .email-header h1 { font-size: 1.8em; color: #00497c; font-weight: 800; margin: 0; }
        .email-header h1 span { color: #82b864; }
        .email-body { color: #384050; font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.7; }
        .email-body p { margin: 15px 0; }
        .btn-confirm {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 45px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0074c7, #00497c);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 116, 199, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-confirm:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 116, 199, 0.4); }
        .email-footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e8edf2; color: #8899aa; font-size: 0.85em; }
        .expire-note { background: #f8fafc; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 12px; color: #6a7a8a; font-size: 0.9em; display: inline-block; }
        .link-box {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e8edf2;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .link-box a { color: #0074c7; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9em; }
        .link-box a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
        <div class="logo">📚</div>
        <h1>Knowledge <span>Learning</span></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
        <h2 style="color: #00497c; font-weight: 700;">Bonjour ! 👋</h2>
        <p>Merci de vous être inscrit sur <strong>Knowledge Learning</strong>.</p>
        <p>Pour activer votre compte, veuillez confirmer votre adresse email en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessous :</p>

        <a href="{{ signedUrl|raw }}" class="btn-confirm">✅ Confirmer mon email</a>

        <div class="expire-note">
            ⏰ Ce lien expirera dans <strong>1 heure</strong>.
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #6a7a8a; font-size: 0.95em;">
            Si vous n'avez pas créé de compte, ignorez simplement cet email.
        </p>

        <div class="link-box">
            <small>🔗 Si le bouton ne fonctionne pas, copiez ce lien :</small><br>
            <a href="{{ signedUrl|raw }}" target="_blank">{{ signedUrl|raw }}</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
            &copy; 2026 <strong>Knowledge Learning</strong> - Tous droits réservés<br>
            <small>Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement.</small>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>